  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/1c33dc4668248dcfe28432c194630c15.avif?t=1773069828\" width=800 height=114 /></span>After receiving a distress call about an explosion, a detective travels to the remote Archdale Castle in search of answers but finds herself trapped. Can you find out what happened? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/2fd0a0be79705388bdbb9358856e586d.poster.avif?t=1773069828\" width=800 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/2fd0a0be79705388bdbb9358856e586d.webm?t=1773069828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/2fd0a0be79705388bdbb9358856e586d.mp4?t=1773069828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Find Notes, Solve Puzzles, and Use Key Items</strong> to progress through haunting <strong>Atmospheric Environments</strong> in this indie <strong>Action Survival Horror</strong>. Use a range of <strong>Firearms, defensive options and Melee Strikes</strong> to take on the horrors that await and <strong>Learn Movement Techniques</strong> & <strong>Upgrade Equipment</strong> that suit your playstyle to prepare for <strong>Intense Boss Battles</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/d1f5d381cbae7bf9abe5a228c8d8c5fa.avif?t=1773069828\" width=800 height=114 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Range of terrifying environments -</strong> From the open sea of the misty docks to the tight crypts of a haunted cemetery. Evil Awaits has a range of terrifyingly atmospheric and realistic environments filled with collectables, keys, puzzles, notes, encounters and surprises.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/f44f82c2d4f6f91a1ef696a1d5c2d7ad.poster.avif?t=1773069828\" width=800 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/f44f82c2d4f6f91a1ef696a1d5c2d7ad.webm?t=1773069828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/f44f82c2d4f6f91a1ef696a1d5c2d7ad.mp4?t=1773069828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Face a diverse horde -</strong> A variety of mutations stand between you and what awaits, all with different move sets & weaknesses. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/0ba549e8ee7dbef5995bbf9f41dc9bd8.poster.avif?t=1773069828\" width=700 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/0ba549e8ee7dbef5995bbf9f41dc9bd8.webm?t=1773069828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/0ba549e8ee7dbef5995bbf9f41dc9bd8.mp4?t=1773069828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Refine your loadout -</strong> A range of melee attacks, defensive options, firearms, and more can be found throughout the Archdale grounds. Everything upgradeable from toolkits you will find along the way. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/ae605577133e62d377d91bcd126ea5c5.poster.avif?t=1773069828\" width=800 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/ae605577133e62d377d91bcd126ea5c5.webm?t=1773069828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/ae605577133e62d377d91bcd126ea5c5.mp4?t=1773069828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cinematic -</strong> Evil Awaits hosts a range of suspenseful cinematic in-game cutscenes, one of many aspects that tell the tale of the Archdale family curse.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/241c89986154c790b3d69436e5dde027.poster.avif?t=1773069828\" width=800 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/241c89986154c790b3d69436e5dde027.webm?t=1773069828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/241c89986154c790b3d69436e5dde027.mp4?t=1773069828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Horror in your control -</strong> An adapted control scheme allows for swapping sides as well as third & first-person aiming. More 'classic' perspectives are to be added in the future.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survive -</strong> A variety of Brutal boss encounters and dangerous hazards lie in wait, can you overcome the challenge?</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/1c33dc4668248dcfe28432c194630c15.avif?t=1773069828\" width=800 height=114 /></span>After receiving a distress call about an explosion, a detective travels to the remote Archdale Castle in search of answers but finds herself trapped. Can you find out what happened? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/2fd0a0be79705388bdbb9358856e586d.poster.avif?t=1773069828\" width=800 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/2fd0a0be79705388bdbb9358856e586d.webm?t=1773069828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/2fd0a0be79705388bdbb9358856e586d.mp4?t=1773069828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Find Notes, Solve Puzzles, and Use Key Items</strong> to progress through haunting <strong>Atmospheric Environments</strong> in this indie <strong>Action Survival Horror</strong>. Use a range of <strong>Firearms, defensive options and Melee Strikes</strong> to take on the horrors that await and <strong>Learn Movement Techniques</strong> & <strong>Upgrade Equipment</strong> that suit your playstyle to prepare for <strong>Intense Boss Battles</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/d1f5d381cbae7bf9abe5a228c8d8c5fa.avif?t=1773069828\" width=800 height=114 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Range of terrifying environments -</strong> From the open sea of the misty docks to the tight crypts of a haunted cemetery. 